1. "*Žalim* što se to dogodilo." (I'm sorry that happened.)

2. "*Žalim* što nisam bio tu da ti pomognem." (I regret not being there to help you.)

3. "*Žalim* da nisam znao za to ranije." (I regret not knowing about it earlier.)

4. "*Žalim* da nisam uspeo da to uradim." (I regret not being able to do it.)

5. "Šta *žališ*?" (What are you sorry about?)